import { useEffect, useState } from "react"; import VehicleData from "../json/vehicle.json" export default function VehicleDetails() { const [moreDetailsShow, setMoreDetailsShow] = useState(true); const [data, setData] = useState(null); useEffect(() => { setData(VehicleData); }, []); return (

Vehicle Details

{/* */}
{moreDetailsShow && data &&

Overall Summary

{data.innerObject.All.Summary.map((summary, index) => (

Enquiry ID: {summary["Enquiry Id"]}

Total Trucks: {summary["Total Trucks"]}

Total Bags: {summary["Total Bags"]}

Unloaded Bags: {summary["Unloaded Bags"]}

Returned Bags: {summary["Returned Bags"]}

Gross Weight: {summary["Gross Weight"]}

Tare Weight: {summary["Tare Weight"]}

Net Weight: {summary["Net Weight"]}

Avg Bag Size: {summary["Avg Bag Size"]}

))}

Individual Vehicle Details

{data.innerObject.All.VehicleList.map((vehicle, index) => (
Truck ID: {vehicle.data["Vehicle No"]}

WBS No: {vehicle.data["WBS No"]}

Weight Details

Total Bags: {vehicle.data["Total Bags"]}

Gross Weight MT: {vehicle.data["Gross Weight MT"]}

Avg Bag Size KG: {vehicle.data["Avg Bag Size KG"]}

Unloading/Weighment Details

Unloaded Bags: {vehicle.data["Unloaded Bags"]}

Tare Weight MT: {vehicle.data["Tare Weight MT"]}

First Weighment Date n Time: {vehicle.data["First Weighment Date n Time"]}

Returned Bags: {vehicle.data["Returned Bags"]}

Net Weight MT: {vehicle.data["Net Weight MT"]}

Final Weighment Date n Time: {vehicle.data["Final Weighment Date n Time"]}

QA Details
{vehicle.obj.QAParameters && vehicle.obj.QAParameters.length > 0 ? ( vehicle.obj.QAParameters.map((qa, qaIndex) => (

Parameter Name: {qa.ParameterName || 'MOISTURE'}

Result: {qa.Result || '4.90'}

)) ) : (

Parameter Name: MOISTURE

Result: 4.90

)}
Loading Details
{vehicle.obj.VehicleUnloadingDetails && vehicle.obj.VehicleUnloadingDetails.length > 0 ? ( vehicle.obj.VehicleUnloadingDetails.map((unload, unloadIndex) => (

Wagon/Stack No: {unload.Name}

Bags: {unload["No Of Bags"]}

)) ) : (

Wagon/Stack No: 31032514111

Bags: {vehicle.data["Total Bags"]}

)}
More Details
))}
}
) }
